claim.claim-text:
1. A cement composition comprising:
(A) cement;
(B) water;
(C) a high-density additive selected from the group consisting of silicon carbide, sintered bauxite, and a combination thereof, wherein the high-density additive is in a concentration in the range of about 30% to about 120% by weight of the cement; and
(D) a fluid loss additive, wherein the fluid loss additive is in a concentration of about 0.1 to about 4% by weight of the cement; and
wherein the cement composition has a density of at least 16 pounds per gallon.
